sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Legacy as Legacy SWS Data
  participant Import as Import Dry Run
  participant Mapping as Department Mapping
  participant Parallel as Parallel Run
  participant Cutover as Controlled Cut-Over
  participant Rollback as Rollback Path
  Legacy->>Import: Export pilot records
  Import->>Mapping: Validate IDs and references
  Mapping->>Parallel: Run mock/sandbox sync
  Parallel->>Cutover: Approve selected case set
  Cutover->>Cutover: Enable adapters and jobs
  Cutover-->>Rollback: Disable adapters and pause workers if needed
